name: Parse Solar Radiation CSV
description: Parses a Vasari solar radiation analysis CSV file and returns lists of absolute and normalized radiation values, their XYZ coordinates and their normals as well as the highest and lowest radiation value and the total of all radiation samples

dependencies.name: Get Highest And Lowest From List
